Title : South Bentinck
Text : '''South Bentinck''' is a [[locality (settlement)|locality]] on [[South Bentinck Arm]] in the [[British Columbia Coast|Central Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]], located on the north side of the mouth of the [[Noeick River]] on the east shore of that inlet.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/40872.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "South Bentinck (locality)"]</ref>

